{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 38 INT. HYATT HOUSE LOBBY -- NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Penny blasts into the Continental Hyatt House, William on her arm.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The lobby of this bastion of seventies rock is more alive than most clubs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's a swirling mass of Roadies carrying Halliburton briefcases plastered with tour stickers, mingling Rockers, and more than a few Groupies with lower-ambitions and taller-platforms than Penny Lane.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The feeling is communal, illicit, intoxicating.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The secret community of rock.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Penny attracts a hailstorm of friends and comrades.
