{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 41 INT. ICE ROOM -- NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The ice machine makes new cubes with a grinding noise.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Penny puts ice in her glass.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Behind her, Russell moves into frame, hands delicately riding the sides of her body.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A motorcycle roars by, just outside the door, as Penny moves away from Russell's exploring hands.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY
{META_DATA}: (with real indignation)
