{DIALOGUE}: The way you pick up strays wherever you go.
{DIALOGUE}: Like Pied Piper.
{META_DATA}: (cube)
{DIALOGUE}: The way you know the words to every song.
{DIALOGUE}: Every song.
{DIALOGUE}: Especially the bad ones.
{DIALOGUE}: Mostly the bad ones.
{META_DATA}: (cube)
{DIALOGUE}: That green coat in the middle of summer.
{META_DATA}: (cube)
{DIALOGUE}: The real name you won't reveal.
{META_DATA}: (cube)
{DIALOGUE}: And.
{DIALOGUE}: I'd keep going, but my glass if full.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY
{META_DATA}: (quietly)
{DIALOGUE}: Damn.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He kisses her powerfully, hands at his sides.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She fights to keep her hands off him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bonham's motorcycle rips by, just outside the door.
