{DIALOGUE}: Lesssssslie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie.
{DIALOGUE}: LESlie.
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She continues saying it until it no longer has meaning.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And finally she sits next to him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY (cont'd)
