{DIALOGUE}: Now.
{DIALOGUE}: Have I helped you get that off your chest?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They kiss.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 60B INT. WILLIAM'S HOTEL ROOM - SAME TIME
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The girls continue their settling-in process.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAPPHIRE
