{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Polexia hangs up, and begins to dial again.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Okay.
{DIALOGUE}: You guys.
{DIALOGUE}: Wait.
{DIALOGUE}: Put down the phone, Polexia.
