{DIALOGUE}: First, this is my room...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAPPHIRE
{DIALOGUE}: Come on, you're a fan like us.
{DIALOGUE}: You're on our side of the line.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Second.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm not Opie.
{DIALOGUE}: Alright?
{DIALOGUE}: Opie is a little boy.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm here to do a job.
{DIALOGUE}: I am a professional.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ESTRELLA
{META_DATA}: (flipping luggage tag)
{DIALOGUE}: Ooooooo, sorry, Mr. 42.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Third!
{META_DATA}: (has their attention now)
{DIALOGUE}: ... this phone is a big, big deal.
{DIALOGUE}: In a minute, I have to go interview Russell.
{DIALOGUE}: Do not answer this phone if it rings.
{DIALOGUE}: I have family members with severe anxiety Problems.
{DIALOGUE}: She will not understand.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: POLEXIA
{META_DATA}: (wounded)
{DIALOGUE}: But what if Ozzy calls Sapphire?
{DIALOGUE}: And I gave Jimmy Page this number.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ESTRELLA
{DIALOGUE}: Or a guy who looked like Jimmy Page.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: William looks at their troubled faces, full of too much-longing and too much make-up.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Okay.
{DIALOGUE}: I have a solution.
{DIALOGUE}: Answer the phone.
{DIALOGUE}: But if anyone without an English accent is on the phone...
{META_DATA}: (winging it)
{DIALOGUE}: Just hang up.
{DIALOGUE}: Or say it's the wrong room.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They nod.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's a good plan.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 61 EXT. HALLWAY -- NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The hanging sign on the door reads: DO NOT DISTURB.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: William knocks on Russell's door.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A maid pushes up against him with her cart, which now blocks the hallway.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: SHOULD I COME BY LATER?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A group of golf conventioneers are now trapped behind the maid cart.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They ease past William as he negotiates with Russell through the door.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RUSSELL (O.S.)
{DIALOGUE}: YES, I'M IN TOO TRUTHFUL A MOOD!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: MAYBE THAT'S A GOOD THING!!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RUSSELL (O.S.)
