{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Estrella panics, hangs up quickly, as if the phone has just caught fire.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ESTRELLA
{DIALOGUE}: I think I just messed up!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 65 INT. RADIO STATION -- NIGHT -- SAME TIME
