{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: What problems?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY
{DIALOGUE}: Okay.
{DIALOGUE}: I got it.
{DIALOGUE}: I think your name should be Spencer, and mine will be Jane.
