{DIALOGUE}: Real people.
{DIALOGUE}: That's all I'm interested in... From here on out.
{DIALOGUE}: What is REAL?
{DIALOGUE}: You're real.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Thanks.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A wave of warmth comes over Russell.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RUSSELL
{DIALOGUE}: You know, you know all about us and I don't know shit about you.
