{DIALOGUE}: Plus -
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RUSSELL
{META_DATA}: (immediately)
{DIALOGUE}: Okay, that's good.
{DIALOGUE}: That's enough.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: It's good to talk about it.
{DIALOGUE}: Really good.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Russel now sees some hero worship in the kid's face, and it makes him nervous.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: Hey, man, maybe we should go back.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RUSSELL
{DIALOGUE}: If they want me, they can find me.
