{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Don't you have any regular friends?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY
{DIALOGUE}: Famous people are just more interesting.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He looks at her.
