{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{META_DATA}: (carefully)
{DIALOGUE}: Well, I would be worried that they were using me.
{DIALOGUE}: And not that anybody's using you, but -
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She swoons a little, touched and moved.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY
{DIALOGUE}: Boy, if this was the real world and some guy talked to me like that -
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Let me finish.
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: I'm not famous....
{DIALOGUE}: but you could always use me.
{DIALOGUE}: If anything happens.
{DIALOGUE}: And I would never use you.
{DIALOGUE}: Even if I got famous.
{DIALOGUE}: So you know, you always have that from me... in the real world.
{DIALOGUE}: If you ever have to go back there, for anything.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She looks at him curiously, as the door blasts open.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sapphire and Polexia head for William.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAPPHIRE
{DIALOGUE}: Your time has come.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Did he call?
{META_DATA}: (realizes their intention)
{DIALOGUE}: What are you -- stop it -- we're talking here.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAPPHIRE
{DIALOGUE}: Pants him.
{DIALOGUE}: Opie must die.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They swarm him, dragging him kicking into the bedroom.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 99 INT. HOTEL BEDROOM -- NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Steely Dan, looking pale and somehow snappy, perform "Do It Again" on The Midnight Special.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The girls force William onto the bed, and envelope him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Their sexuality is fun, untroubled.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Shot moves past bodies crossing frame, onto William's face.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON PENNY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Across room, sitting and watching.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAPPHIRE
{DIALOGUE}: Just relax.
{DIALOGUE}: Take a vacation from yourself.
{DIALOGUE}: Leave this to professionals.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Estrella and Polexia kiss each other playfully.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: William looks confused.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Across the room, Penny laughs, turns up the TV, blows him a kiss.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Penny's eyes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Across the room.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His eyes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His sexual awakening may be downtime amusement for them, but to him it's an embarrassingly intense moment he shares only with Penny Lane -- across the room.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She turns away, smiling, disappears into the next room.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ON STEELY DAN
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: On the television.
{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 99A INT. BEDROOM - NIGHT - TWENTY MINUTES LATER - HANDHELD
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Post-sex pajama party.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sapphire, Estrella, and Polexia girltalk about their first rock and roll conquests.
