{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It hasn't sunk in yet.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Russell produces a piece of hotel stationery.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He reads a poem.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RUSSELL
{DIALOGUE}: So Penny our friend has gained another year.
