{DIALOGUE}: You're worried about me and Russell.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah.
{DIALOGUE}: I gotta work on that.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY
{DIALOGUE}: You're so sweet.
{DIALOGUE}: God -- if there was more of you in him...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
