{CHARACTER_NAME}: JEFF
{DIALOGUE}: Leslie!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DICK
{DIALOGUE}: Your room is completely stocked, far away from any noisy ice machines, elevators or maid quarters.
{DIALOGUE}: The air- conditioning is already on.
