{CHARACTER_NAME}: RIC
{META_DATA}: (whispers)
{DIALOGUE}: It's all happening.
{DIALOGUE}: Zeppelin is at the Plaza.
{DIALOGUE}: So's four other bands.
{DIALOGUE}: They're partying up there right now.
{DIALOGUE}: Sapphire, and Miss Penny Lane too... She wants you to call her.
