{DIALOGUE}: We made it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The band nods solemnly, importantly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JEFF (cont'd)
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: Damn it -- I'm gonna enjoy this.
{DIALOGUE}: The first time I bought that magazine The Beatles were on the cover.
{DIALOGUE}: Four of them.
{DIALOGUE}: Four of us.
{DIALOGUE}: Together.
{DIALOGUE}: TOGETHER!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They begin singing the then-current Dr. Hook and the Medicine Show hit, "The Cover of the Rolling Stone" to William.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LESLIE
