{DIALOGUE}: She's not with any of you, is she?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM/DICK
{DIALOGUE}: She's with me.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And now Leslie has confirmation.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A symphony of looks, as Dick gets to his feet and moves to confront Penny.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Penny Lane's eyes fill and she runs out.
