{DIALOGUE}: She named you Lady?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY
{DIALOGUE}: Lady Goodman.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: No.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PENNY
{DIALOGUE}: You never really get used to it, either.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WILLIAM
{DIALOGUE}: Well -- this -- this just explains everything.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He wishes it did.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She rubs her stomach.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's a rocky morning.
