{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Music continues.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ON AIRPLANE DEPARTURE SCHEDULE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: William's finger finds San Francisco.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 149 INT. CAB -- SAN FRANCISCO -- DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The kid checks the address as he arrives at the MJB Building, and its next-door neighbor, the San Francisco headquarters of Rolling Stone Magazine.
